						<div class="postbody">I have the SNES Miracle Piano, and it has jacks in the back where you can hook it up to a regular MIDI-capable computer, via the standard MIDI cables.
<br />
<br />It's not GM though, so the instruments are all in a different order than they otherwise would be on a GM device, but none the less, the piano behaves just like any normal MIDI device would, at least when you hook it up to a computer. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />-Drag</div>
